9VajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=78231a47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence</a><br />\n<br />\n方法:<br />\n1. 填晒名同email<br />\n2. 禁Sign Now<br />\n3. 登入自己登記嘅email，搵白宫網站send黎嘅確認email，禁確認就得<br />\n<br />\n順便推介埋呢個網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7dd9d259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a><br />\n佢有曬而家同香港示威相關嘅白宮聯署 加埋中文翻譯<br />\n<br />\n點用，睇呢個:<br />\n【國際戰線】痴撚線手足整咗個中文版聯署機！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827349</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n打好國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"bddd94ff885762dad0b48958081fb7ec118908ba","tid":1967534,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:17:21.000Z","msg":"除咗呢堆，重有呢堆<br />\n<br />\n麻煩推上熱門，因為我搵到10個白宮聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1960942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1960942</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8643a7dd6667911847f4649d97b86de0b445ce73","tid":1967534,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"68e1cd68e6453326fb60065d3232e50e05878d1c","tid":1967534,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7613075d68631754a3892569e2289cc82da99681","tid":1967534,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"032076ad370c27461d8d0629e355f438d209c15f","tid":1967534,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:18:27.000Z","msg":"第2次推"},{"pid":"87a67e4f2d50179b0b2aedea862208c233035221","tid":1967534,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"